data.description: *Open House Saturday, April 13th from 1pm - 4pm*     Welcome to this stunning home nestled in the sought-after neighborhood of Riverstone at Alamo Ranch! The stately stone and brick exterior exudes elegance and charm, setting the stage for a warm welcome as you step onto the inviting front porch, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or unwinding to the sounds of the evening. Situated on a cul-de-sac with no rear neighbors, this 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home offers privacy and tranquility. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a spacious formal dining area that seamlessly connects to the kitchen, enhancing the flow of the home and providing ample space for entertaining. Alternatively, transform the dining space into a room that suits your lifestyle, without sacrificing seating thanks to the convenient eat-in kitchen.The kitchen is a culinary delight, offering ample cabinet and counter space, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, gas cooking, a corner pantry, and a breakfast bar. A striking stone and brick fireplace serves as the focal point of the spacious living area, offering cozy ambiance for gatherings or quiet evenings curled up with a book. Upstairs, escape to the luxurious primary suite complete with a walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom boasting a dual sink vanity, soaking tub, and standalone walk-in shower. Three additional bedrooms, a sizable loft, and a convenient laundry room complete the upper level. Outside, the expansive backyard is perfect for hosting Texas BBQs or enjoying summer nights around a fire pit. Residents of Riverstone at Alamo Ranch enjoy access to unbeatable amenities including a playground, pool, basketball court, and more. Conveniently located with easy access to major thoroughfares, this home offers a quick commute to shopping, dining, and entertainment. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home sweet home!
